context.name: Sundus Shafqat
context.bio: Sundus is a junior year student majoring in IDS  hoping to pursue a career in data analytics. She is on the board for FCG as a project manager where she works closely with upper management to ensure the scope and direction for each project is on schedule. She is passionate to learn more about consulting and how to tackle case interviews through the resources provided by FCG.
